@elonmusk Genuine question: 

Why, when those behind Neuralink, could have chosen ANY NAME IN THE WORLD, did they chose "Neuralink", which, in Greek Isopsephy adds up to 666, for a company that is creating exactly what is described in the Book of Revelations about the mark of the beast? 

Could you not have chosen another name or spelling? Even Neurolink, would have made the numerical value different. 

Was this deliberate? Accident? Or was this prophecy?

Companies put enormous thought in to their name, spelling of that name etc.   Was this a consideration? 

@grok please put the Greek Isopsephy total for the word "Neuralink" and the passage of Revelations where it talks of a mark on the forehead and right hand, that people wont be able to buy or sell without the mark, and the number of the mark.
